#####################################################

Sample for testing ESB Scheduled tasks


#####################################################
Steps to use:

1. Copy this jar to the repository/components/lib folder and restart the server

Follow the Doc http://docs.wso2.org/display/ESB470/Configure+with+WSO2+Message+Broker to configure wso2 MB with ESB
a. Make sure to up MB with Portoffset 1
b. Copy required MB client jars to repository/components/lib folder
c. Add jndi.properties file to repository/conf folder   

2. Go the Scheduled Tasks page on esb
3. Add a task 
4. Enter Task Implementation  as org.wso2.carbon.esb.task.SampleMessageRecieverTask
5. Schedule the Trigger appropriately

Now you should see subscriptions creating for queue "taskqueue"
